Usage: dbSet [-help] [-d] 
             {<obj>|<objList>|head|top|selected}[.<objType>]...{.<attrName>} 
             <attrValue>

-help            # Prints out the command usage 
-d               # User specified values are in database units, in integer. 
                 # Default: All values are in user units, in microns. (bool, optional) 
{<obj>|<objList>|head|top|selected}[.<objType>]...{.<attrName>} 
                 # DB object-hierarchy-string. 
                 # {<obj>|<objList>|head|top|selected}: Specifies the starting 
                 # point for the query; <objType>: Specifies the object type; 
                 # <attrName>: Specifies the object attribute to change. 
                 # (string, required) 
<attrValue>      # Specifies the new attribute value. (string, required)